::Spears::

Despite the fact she was in stasis, her programs were still 
fighting.  Smoke ribboned out of her neck and head gear.  A few 
sparks came out of her shoulder where she got hit.  Her optics 
flickered and dimmed slightly.  Her trainer side was over powering 
her maximal side.  Her trainer side was trying to over power the 
device that kept her in stasis lock.  She body shook and jerked as 
the trainer program was winning.
